title: Kimi no Iru Machi - Fantasy Chapter 200 - Ch. 05
description:
Fantasy Chapter 200 is a series of special chapters released with the Kimi no Iru Machi anime Blu-ray sets. Chapter 200 features Haruto and Yuzuki's first time, and the fantasy chapters are alternate versions featuring other female characters selected by a popularity poll.
